{"tid":347232,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男友對我已經失去新鮮感","createTime":"2017-08-04T15:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T11:52:48.000Z","uid":133548,"like":7,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a89d89704216cc240e45fc8e817b6ab24fc94ec3","tid":347232,"uid":133548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:37:06.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左年幾<br />\n<br />\n我第二次拍拖 對上一次係中學啲puppy love<br />\n宜家對佢好依賴 好中意佢 第一次都係比左佢 <br />\n一開始嘅時候 我地兩個都好痴纏 會成日掛住對方<br />\n但過左兩三個月 佢已經對我冷淡左<br />\n個陣成日喺到諗 點解佢嘅熱戀期完得咁快<br />\n自己仲傻更更咁處於熱戀期狀態 無時無刻都想見到佢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地有keep住搞嘢 啱啱一齊個陣幾乎日日都搞(當時放緊暑假)<br />\n但慢慢就越黎越少 試過問佢點解會咁 佢話因爲攰 以前放假唔使翻學翻工 好精力 宜家要翻學翻工好攰 <br />\n<br />\n但係同左佢一齊之後先知自己係淫底 成日都好想要<br />\n會忍唔摸佢 挑逗佢 比曬明示暗示佢 甚至講埋出口話想要 <br />\n不過佢都會無反應 又或者拒絕我 而當佢想要個陣 就同我搞或者會叫我用口 我都無拒絕過<br />\n<br />\n有時候會好難過 因為好似乞求佢搞我咁 而今日就更難過 <br />\n我主動話想幫佢含 佢話唔想要 又係因為攰 之後可能講到佢有啲扯 於是又話好 點知用口用左一陣佢話都係算 因為含到有啲痛(我個下真係聽到頹左) 而且仲話佢細佬仲未準備好 事後問翻佢點解宜家摸佢條J同挑逗佢都無反應 唔會扯 搞到啱先幫佢含都咁 佢竟然答因爲我平時成日都摸架啦 直頭當玩具咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以啱先含之前摸佢佢都唔扯無乜反應咁<br />\n<br />\n咁我係咪應該控制下自己 平時唔好係咪都摸佢條J 搞到佢宜家對我無曬感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765a3f2d633777c0125589dd9697e5957d032562","tid":347232,"uid":64582,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"搵SP,完"},{"pid":"2f6998b89610b333e3860870781dcc9b6afbf56c","tid":347232,"uid":132488,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"佢應該係鍾意返女仔"},{"pid":"a039e34b594f96cf4119f524e01c9df99d15cc9d","tid":347232,"uid":44504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:42:04.000Z","msg":"技術問題"},{"pid":"c5266c429c556424d4fa7a08c35d4766daa248bf","tid":347232,"uid":133548,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢應該係鍾意返女仔</blockquote><br />\n我係真絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3b78d98e68d28f7ce8e1be1afcef3fdb977250","tid":347232,"uid":133548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:53:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>技術問題</blockquote><br />\n但之前幫佢用口佢都話舒服同埋射得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd1fb4fc32bb430903b983ede8e3ca81a7fce9e","tid":347232,"uid":124037,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:54:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢應該係鍾意返女仔</blockquote><br />\n講得好"},{"pid":"b138d0c662220153ba63b6d76302ffebeada9f06","tid":347232,"uid":126648,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:54:49.000Z","msg":"扑到厭左<br />\n一係有第二個<br />\n講完"},{"pid":"81e784e91e7286419864ad395ccc751a7d2a30ce","tid":347232,"uid":37005,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:55:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢應該係鍾意返女仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82b3b1128f4155d40b65205f6a4c78c93095940","tid":347232,"uid":20882,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:55:23.000Z","msg":"未扯嘅賓周真係好得意"},{"pid":"9933e38d3600233c49363c5b704b23aa245a911d","tid":347232,"uid":116609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:55:49.000Z","msg":"冇情調/冇調情？"},{"pid":"034a06b2c4c193ee3e8f4a6ef80d485ffa1cc4d7","tid":347232,"uid":13809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0acfddd0c3d95458544d142c4831fa728a7e985d","tid":347232,"uid":28800,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0f30e0ccd96243fc91e48e3a17fe74d015a8b99","tid":347232,"uid":37005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"你覺得佢係因為你太大食而對你冷淡 而唔係已經唔再鍾意你?"},{"pid":"de3e70636d16bfa5374fd49caab1929c80367542","tid":347232,"uid":10544,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:57:11.000Z","msg":"唔用保鮮紙既後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40eae0a946391e0d867b33fe7940f8260c245342","tid":347232,"uid":80529,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T15:59:22.000Z","msg":"自己拍緊，已經6年幾，keep到仲好緊好痴對方<br />\n其實唔係單一方面嘅問題<br />\n有時可能你太緊佢，佢又會覺得煩<br />\n自不然唔想理你<br />\n當然最大可能就係，已經食左你隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7acf00d8c762ef2986dc135679db1ca06c70fd8","tid":347232,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:00:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00059dfb9926274bfc33ee8901348a90236cbdd8","tid":347232,"uid":34181,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:15:30.000Z","msg":"過來人答你<br />\n<br />\n做慣左已經冇乜大感覺<br />\n與其你繼續鑽研係生理上刺激佢<br />\n不如諗下點樣係心理上更加刺激到佢啦<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知佢有乜咩特別既性癖好？<br />\n黑絲？制服？腳交？<br />\n了解下佢平時睇開咩類型既AV，<br />\n可能會對你更加有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n另外，適當既前戲都好緊要，<br />\n探索下佢身體其他既敏感點，<br />\n唔好一嚟就摩打手打J，<br />\n咁樣搞馬撚都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n記住，心理因素大過生理因素。<br />\n否則你既作用同一個飛機杯冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f0dd205fc46a3ee44bbec8713276b1016f60ece","tid":347232,"uid":133548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未扯嘅賓周真係好得意</blockquote><br />\n無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88282f8bdb2a05183971e86b62ed740fce7b4314","tid":347232,"uid":133548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇情調/冇調情？</blockquote><br />\n無 可以點調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d32c4e66ba3383fdd24f01cdb55ffda3f3a79485","tid":347232,"uid":133548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:43:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扑得咁密你唔悶咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係唔覺悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d29a136f3d5e4c4839bdb7eaa895639d10280bdb","tid":347232,"uid":133548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:49:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你覺得佢係因為你太大食而對你冷淡 而唔係已經唔再鍾意你?</blockquote><br />\n我覺得係佢性格係咁 覺得段感情已經變得好平凡所以冷淡左 無左以前熱戀嘅感覺 之前有傾過 佢話唔係所有嘢都唔會變 時間耐左就點都會有唔同左 但我就唔認同 點解時間長就等於會變？"},{"pid":"74c81b2fab0906e94d3e36cbabd621306e0bd749","tid":347232,"uid":133548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己拍緊，已經6年幾，keep到仲好緊好痴對方<br />\n其實唔係單一方面嘅問題<br />\n有時可能你太緊佢，佢又會覺得煩<br />\n自不然唔想理你<br />\n當然最大可能就係，已經食左你隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得係咁 身邊朋友都話我將佢睇得太重 太緊佢 而佢又唔緊張我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1add37e49dbbedc941733cadfa1f5a378066f7bb","tid":347232,"uid":133548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T16:55:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過來人答你<br />\n<br />\n做慣左已經冇乜大感覺<br />\n與其你繼續鑽研係生理上刺激佢<br />\n不如諗下點樣係心理上更加刺激到佢啦<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知佢有乜咩特別既性癖好？<br />\n黑絲？制服？腳交？<br />\n了解下佢平時睇開咩類型既AV，<br />\n可能會對你更加有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n另外，適當既前戲都好緊要，<br />\n探索下佢身體其他既敏感點，<br />\n唔好一嚟就摩打手打J，<br />\n咁樣搞馬撚都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n記住，心理因素大過生理因素。<br />\n否則你既作用同一個飛機杯冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係咁中意呢啲性癖好 但會買啲性感啲嘅bra同under黎著比佢睇 佢幾中意 不過都係有啲厭咁<br />\n<br />\n前戲都有 弊在有時挑逗佢都無反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af04f3ab97320f1c762e12cadda8418508e374cb","tid":347232,"uid":53903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:00:09.000Z","msg":"咁真係會攰架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305952a68d77ff5ac7feac18513aa136dc90e24e","tid":347232,"uid":125467,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"我都試過 個ex 係咁<br />\n但個時係拍左年幾拖 <br />\n愈黎愈少搞 就算佢硬晒 <br />\n我聊佢 <br />\n佢都話要訓教 <br />\n真係勁頹"},{"pid":"c87f03f4cbdf5cb4943266943f57ce99d4f60503","tid":347232,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"涼透心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f6484264935481a1845b31c838abbb1e5d16d27","tid":347232,"uid":133548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:10:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁真係會攰架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該都係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1233960004d7d874c17144c0c8d656ea25b6f0","tid":347232,"uid":133548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都試過 個ex 係咁<br />\n但個時係拍左年幾拖 <br />\n愈黎愈少搞 就算佢硬晒 <br />\n我聊佢 <br />\n佢都話要訓教 <br />\n真係勁頹</blockquote><br />\n我都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢硬曬都唔搞"},{"pid":"5ac237bc85443544627c7048ddba9510285bdd19","tid":347232,"uid":350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:19:17.000Z","msg":"佢唔愛你<br />\n只係一時感覺同你一齊<br />\n好明顯<br />\n無可能兩三個月就淡"},{"pid":"9e5c8a6e616d3a9c3aff14fd9b3e27acbc949125","tid":347232,"uid":59641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:21:25.000Z","msg":"佢係咪有啲隱藏性癖﹐例如sm果啲咁﹐對有果類性癖嘅人普通sex其實冇乜癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe493dc5a8e64ddda6cbf0c5bc03d9f87e28ae28","tid":347232,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:22:53.000Z","msg":"臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b2de6a25e0ba2c2300cde8cd9cf5a2fbcdf164","tid":347232,"uid":93620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T17:30:08.000Z","msg":"所以覺得唔可以咁快搞，起碼一齊一年至兩年先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太快就搞段感情會易變質，男仔追女動力都係為了搞野，一齊耐咗知佢真心先搞，都會keep得耐"},{"pid":"9c9a32184396409efa13d63c8053ac52ccd6c6e5","tid":347232,"uid":37427,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T21:57:31.000Z","msg":"我有d似你男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望唔係真啦<br />\n我開頭同女友都係差唔多日日見<br />\n但見得太多會麻木<br />\n結果有排我要去外國做2個星期野<br />\n番到黎水溫又高番<br />\n<br />\n除左見太多會麻木，另一個原因係覺得穩定左，可以專注係其他地方上面，好像專業，為未來打算之類<br />\n<br />\n另外樓上講心理&gt;生理係無錯既<br />\n而且係勁work<br />\n<br />\n話說有既女友醉左扮貓主動搞我<br />\n果晚巨龍獸係成功進化成究極巨龍獸的<br />\n<br />\n不過我怕羞就緊係無講出黎啦<br />\n之後同佢搞野都好似為搞而搞，反而唔想掂佢<br />\n<br />\n總結：見少d，了解男人，心理&gt;生理"},{"pid":"873b666b178860defd98549aee9f719721013f0e","tid":347232,"uid":80529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自己拍緊，已經6年幾，keep到仲好緊好痴對方<br />\n其實唔係單一方面嘅問題<br />\n有時可能你太緊佢，佢又會覺得煩<br />\n自不然唔想理你<br />\n當然最大可能就係，已經食左你隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得係咁 身邊朋友都話我將佢睇得太重 太緊佢 而佢又唔緊張我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以要時緊時放，如果你男友返工嘅更加唔好太緊張，要照顧兩邊會好大壓力好煩<br />\n第二樣嘢好重要但返唔到轉頭嘅，咁快俾隻豬人<br />\n可能你會話我封建又追唔到潮流<br />\n但你諗下，一件你可以試玩禮物，唔啱有得退<br />\n同一件我等七,八年先買得拆得嘅禮物，邊樣期待啲襟玩啲？"},{"pid":"aecf91fc3ee74128c971c38d388abddc155e5c3f","tid":347232,"uid":46281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,